priority: 1
face-image: img/rathenau.jpg

= <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Walther Rathenau**</span> shot dead!

While being chauffeured from his house in Berlin-Grundewald to the foreign office, a group of terrorist's operating under what they call <span style="color: #808080;">**Organisation Consul**</span> conducted a drive by, with one opening fire at close range at <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Rathenau**</span>, killing him instantly. Another threw a hand granade into the car, destroying it completely, with the chaueffeur also dying. Protests have broken out across the nation because of this, in respect of <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Rathenau**</span>. A nationwide ban on <span style="color: #808080;">**Organisation Consul**</span> has been enforced by the government, and, Chancellor <span style="color: #000000;">**Joseph Wirth**</span>, during the memorial ceremony, stated: "There is the enemy – and there is no doubt about it: The enemy is on the <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**right**</span>!". Though a valiant speech, this does nothing to help his already weak relations with the supposedly "democratic" <span style="color: #C0A054;">**right**</span>.


- @defend_repub_1: Defend <span style="color: #000000;">**Repu**</span><span style="color: #C00000;">**blic**</span><span style="color: #D3C24D;">**anism**</span>.
- @defend_repub_2: Defend <span style="color: #000000;">**Repu**</span><span style="color: #C00000;">**blic**</span><span style="color: #D3C24D;">**anism**</span> and the government.
- @improve_left: Improve our relations with the left.
- @mourn: There is nothing we can do except mourn his death.

@defend_repub_1
on-arrival: ddp_relation += 3; z_relation += 3; pro_republic += 2
subtitle: We are, after all, the party of the <span style="color: #000000;">**Re**</span><span style="color: #C00000;">**pub**</span><span style="color: #D3C24D;">**lic**</span>.

We show that we are commited to democracy.

@defend_repub_2
on-arrival: ddp_relation += 9; z_relation += 9; kpd_relation -= 4; dvp_relation -= 2; uspd_relation += 1; pro_republic += 2
subtitle: The left of our party isnt happy we would side with the bourgeois if we do this.

We show that we stand firmly behind the <span style="color: #000000;">**Re**</span><span style="color: #C00000;">**pub**</span><span style="color: #D3C24D;">**lic**</span> and the coalition.

