@contact_uspd
on-arrival: uspd_relation += 7; left_dissent -= 2; left_strength += 2
subtitle: We are on the way to reunification, so why not?

The <span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span> is largely open towards cooperation with us, given their falling vote share.

@contact_kpd
on-arrival: kpd_relation += 2; left_dissent -= 2; left_strength += 4; reformist_dissent += 3; ddp_relation -= 4
subtitle: The bourgeois and our reformist wing wont be happy about this..

The <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span> is reluctant to cooperate with us, and our reformist faction is outraged.

@contact_both
on-arrival: uspd_relation += 5; kpd_relation += 1; left_dissent -= 2; left_strength += 3; reformist_dissent += 6
subtitle: The reformist faction will be outraged by this, maybe permanently.

The <span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span> is largely open towards cooperation with us, the span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span> is more reluctant. Our reformist faction is outraged, maybe permanently.

@mourn
on-arrival: ddp_relation += 3; z_relation += 3; pro_republic += 1
subtitle: Some think this would be a more prudent option, we cant capitalize on the death of a man so soon, right?

People are still mourning him, and it is a fresh thought.
